  31 May 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  xinit-1.0.2-r4.ebuild:
  (#133671) xterm in RDEPEND causes a circular dependency with
  >=virtual/x11-7. Move it to PDEPEND.

