*xinit-1.0.2-r3 (21 Apr 2006)

  21 Apr 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; files/xdm.start,
  -xinit-1.0.2-r2.ebuild, +xinit-1.0.2-r3.ebuild:
